  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Underground_Guardian_Riddle
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Underground Guardian
  _lines:
  - Far from the sun, you reach the cradle of the realm of Flesh. Every creature that ever walked above is gathered here below, held in the patient dark.
  - The stone forgets nothing. It takes what the living leave behind and keeps its shape for an age of ages.
  - Answer me this, and prove you understand my realm. When bone is laid down and stone closes over it, and time presses the two as one, what remains?
  - Bring me your answer, and the Fragment of Flesh will be yours.
